{"name":"Witcher School","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 3rd level, you choose a witcher school whose techniques and style you wish to employ. Choose between the School of the Wolf, Bear, Cat, Griffin, or Viper, detailed at the end of this class description. The school you choose grants you features at 3rd level, then again at 7th, 10th, and 14th level.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"witcher%20school_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_3_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"653d99a946f42ccb62be5217dc5e9f1b04a3b651"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740078,"modifiedTime":1682004740078,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"000x0TWxm4PjOH1Q"}
{"name":"Quick Wits","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 13th level, you are quick to act and ready to leap into combat at an opportune time. When you roll initiative, you may roll the d20 twice and choose which roll to use.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"quick%20wits_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_13_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"2028faab09beb6976fd78907f3fbc48be0074fad"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740242,"modifiedTime":1682004740242,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"0WcX93xbnAcZdb3p"}
{"name":"Alchemy Expertise","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 18th level, you have mastered efficiently using materials and recycling components in your alchemical crafts. You ignore crafting components when creating Alchemy products. Additionally, you can carry 3 products at a time, instead of 2. When you gain this feature, you learn 4 new <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/optionalfeatures.html#blankhash,flstsource:null=1,flstfeature%20type:witcher%3ar=1\">Alchemy recipes</a> of your choice.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"alchemy%20expertise_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_18_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"d272a59a3ebb7fe29973ecda19c57a1f81006a71"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740340,"modifiedTime":1682004740340,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"1j0EZJWA5VCiqFuZ"}
