{"name":"Adrenaline Rush","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 20th level, you can utilize your adrenaline to burst into a rush of action. At the end of your turn, if you have 5 focus available, you can choose to immediately take another turn; at the end of that turn, you lose all focus. Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"adrenaline%20rush_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_20_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"77342240416d114cb4be3764127ebaf3deda1dd0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740361,"modifiedTime":1682004740361,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"8e5CCir1tSKgkkMh"}
{"name":"Mutations","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As a witcher, you have undergone mutations to your body including the perilous Trial of the Grasses. Starting at 1st level, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Your walking speed is increased by 5 feet. At 10th level, this bonus increases to 10 feet. At 18th level, this bonus increases to 20 feet, and you gain a climbing speed equal to your walking speed.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have @sense[darkvision], up to a range of 30 feet. At 10th level, this range increases to 60 feet. At 18th level, this range increases to 120 feet, and you also gain @sense[blindsight] to a range of 30 feet.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on Wisdom (@skill[Perception]) and Wisdom (@skill[Survival]) checks based on smell.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You are immune to natural diseases.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You are completely sterile - you can have no children through natural means.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Your lifespan is extended dramatically - you age at a rate 10 times slower than regular members of your race.</li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"mutations_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_1_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6493ae831fb03da3cdf3267a1688998ee318c17e"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740006,"modifiedTime":1682004740006,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"8uaeePAlecUDel31"}
{"name":"Slippery","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 7th level, you are hard to keep in place and adept at escaping sticky situations. You can expend 1 focus to use @action[Disengage] or @action[Dash] as a bonus action; if you do, you can also remove the @condition[restrained] or @condition[grappled] condition from yourself.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 7 (School of the Viper)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"slippery_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20viper_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_7_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"0c1dfe6ac8dc46974a10d6b648ca4d7d19889091"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739511,"modifiedTime":1682004739511,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"Afo6nKzKBW5ICZsT"}
{"name":"Battle Signs","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 11th level, you can incorporate signs more easily into your assault. When you take the @action[Attack] action on your turn, you can cast a sign without forgoing any of your weapon attacks. Additionally, at the end of each of your turns, if you haven't cast a sign this turn, you gain 1 focus.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"battle%20signs_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_11_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"3a04316b6c3912664fc1a4d91f9163e2eb13e834"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740223,"modifiedTime":1682004740223,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"AtidpZUUxUsQh8Zy"}
{"name":"School of the Viper","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Based in an unknown location and possibly dissolved, the School of the Viper is a secretive organization, its students few and scattered. The school is known for doing whatever needs to be done for a contract, specializing in hit and run tactics some may call dirty fighting.</p><div data-source=\"johnofbohemia:Witcher\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3370\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Witcher Class\">Dual Wielder</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Starting at 3rd level, you can adopt the traditional two-weapon fighting technique of the Viper School. You can ignore the somatic requirement of signs while using two-weapon fighting; additionally, you gain the <a href=\"https://5e.tools/optionalfeatures.html#two-weapon%20fighting_phb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Two Weapon Fighting</a> fighting style.</p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 3 (School of the Viper)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"school%20of%20the%20viper_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20viper_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_3_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8710ba15a7168c75394fcc6e273d13d5ad97bf70"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739461,"modifiedTime":1682004739461,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"AupD2rMqAGAGrpTc"}
{"name":"Extra Attack","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Beginning at 5th level, you can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the @action[Attack] action on your turn.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/spear-tips-triple-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"extra%20attack_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_5_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"12673238c5e311197a294ae233292b522576f798"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740098,"modifiedTime":1682004740098,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"EacFRSYDVVgIXkGr"}
{"name":"Deadly Flurry","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At level 14, you can use your focus to unleash a flurry of blows. When you take the @action[Attack] action, you can expend 3 focus to make two additional weapon attacks as part of that action.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a long rest or critically strike with a weapon attack.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 14 (School of the Cat)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"deadly%20flurry_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20cat_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_14_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6259a3ff1ff245dd93f5e2507ece55cd353013b5"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739792,"modifiedTime":1682004739792,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"EgGqvsI98xFCTlIy"}
{"name":"School of the Cat","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>The only school known to accept contracts on humans, the School of the Cat has largely become ostracized by their fellow witchers for this breach of their honor code. The school's effectiveness, however, cannot be doubted. Aggressive and flexible, the school focuses on landing many strikes to exploit weaknesses while avoiding damage through mobility.</p><div data-source=\"johnofbohemia:Witcher\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3372\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Witcher Class\">Improved Critical</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Starting at 3rd level, you critical strike on a roll of 19 or 20 on the d20. Additionally, when you critically strike you gain focus up to your cap.</p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 3 (School of the Cat)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"school%20of%20the%20cat_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20cat_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_3_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","ha