{"name":"Quick Reflexes","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 7th level, you are quick to respond to threats and retreat. When a creature makes an attack roll against you, you can choose to consume 1 focus and use your reaction to impose disadvantage on that attack. As a part of the same reaction, you can move 10 feet without provoking opportunity attacks.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When a creature makes an attack roll against you, you can choose to consume 1 focus and use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 7 (School of the Cat)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"quick%20reflexes_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20cat_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_7_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6a6b6e07786212137b9cb8851c5387c8c363d5c2"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739753,"modifiedTime":1682004739753,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"J0q8wcSKDl3x77R0"}
{"name":"Vitalic Blows","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 7th level, you can imbue your strikes with your own vigor; when you hit with a melee weapon attack, you can expend 2 focus to spend one of your hit dice and add it to your damage on that attack. Starting at 14th level, you can choose to expend 2 hit dice instead. When you use your Vitalic Blows feature, you can make a Shove attack as a bonus action for the rest of the turn.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 7 (School of the Bear)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"vitalic%20blows_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20bear_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_7_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"340c683e6a3174d28f678b383b10fd9049dd7346"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739631,"modifiedTime":1682004739631,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"JedGk6frDhXK5VHJ"}
{"name":"Signs","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 2nd level, you are able to channel your focus to cast a few simple but practical magic hexes used by witchers called signs. You can cast a sign in place of a weapon attack when you take the @action[Attack] action on your turn. Casting a sign costs 1 focus, and you can only cast one sign on your turn. You can't cast a sign while holding something in each hand or wielding a weapon with the two-handed property.</p><p>Signs are considered level 1 evocation spells with somatic components for the purposes of other magical effects, and are not considered weapon attacks.</p><p>You learn two signs at 2nd level, and another at 5th, 9th, and 13th level.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3379\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Saving Throws</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>The saving throw DC is calculated as follows:</p><p></p><div class=\"text-center\"><b>Sign save DC</b> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Wisdom modifier</div><p></p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3380\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Aard</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You blow a powerful burst of air at a creature within 15 feet. It must make a Strength saving throw or be pushed 10 feet back and knocked @condition[prone]. When empowered, all creatures in a 5 foot radius sphere around you are affected instead.</p><p>You can also cast the @spell[Gust] cantrip at will.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3381\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Axii</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You attempt to cloud the mind of a creature within 15 feet. It must make a Wisdom saving throw; on a failed save, the creature has disadvantage on the first attack it makes until the end of its next turn. A creature immune to being @condition[charmed] automatically succeeds on its save. When empowered, the affected creature loses its first attack entirely.</p><p>You can also cast the @spell[Friends] cantrip at will.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3382\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Igni</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You blast flames at a creature within 15 feet. It must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking [[/r 2d6]] fire damage on a failed save or half that on a successful save. When empowered, all creatures in a 15 foot cone are affected instead.</p><p>This damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] at 5th([[/r 3d6]]), 11th([[/r 4d6]]), and 17th([[/r 5d6]]) level.</p><p>You can also cast the @spell[Control Flames] cantrip at will.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3383\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Quen</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You place a protective shield on yourself. For the next minute, the first time you take damage from a weapon attack, that damage is reduced by [[/r 1d8]]. When empowered, you can cast this as a reaction to being attacked.</p><p>This reduction increases by [[/r 1d8]] at 5th([[/r 2d8]]), 11th([[/r 3d8]]), and 17th([[/r 4d8]]) level.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3384\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Yrden</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You place down a magical circle with a radius of 10 feet around you that lasts one minute. Inside the circle is difficult terrain for hostile creatures and enemies resistant to only nonmagical damage lose this ability. When empowered, all ranged attacks from hostile creatures made into the circle from without are made with disadvantage.</p></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When empowered, you can cast this"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"Witcher 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"signs_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_2_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"d66735b3c10955fa813a7ee2d33d74fdab4caa55"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740058,"modifiedTime":1682004740058,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"KKyuvA3JCbAOho2K"}
{"name":"Sign Intensity","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 7th level, you can channel additional energy into your signs to grant them new applications. When you cast a sign, you can expend 1 extra focus to add an extra effect as listed below.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3374\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Aard</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Creatures that fail their saving throw against your Aard sign also take [[/r 1d10]] cold damage and have their movement reduced in half until the end of their next turn.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3375\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Axii</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>A creature that fails its saving throw against your Axii sign has disadvantage on all saves to maintain its concentration on a spell until the end of its next turn.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3376\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Igni</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Creatures that fail their saving throw against your Igni sign drop any weapons or held items made of metal or flammable materials. Creatures resistant to fire damage are unaffected by this.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3377\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Quen</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>A creature that triggers your Quen shield with a melee attack is pushed back 5 feet. If the attack's damage is reduced to zero, the attacker is also knocked @condition[prone].</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3378\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Yrden</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Hostile creatures take [[/r 1d12]] force damage when they start their turns inside or enter the circle.</p></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d12","force"],["1d10","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 7 (School of the Griffin)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"sign%20intensity_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_school%20of%20the%20griffin_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_7_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"93fa77b986747100bcdbf38c20ebfaa9250e0486"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004739872,"modifiedTime":1682004739872,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"L3p1yN4Xu6Nj82Wu"}
{"name":"Foil","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 17th level, you are capable of interrupting the spells and abilities of your opponents. When a creature forces you or a friendly creature to make a saving throw, you can use your reaction to make a weapon attack against it. If your attack successfully hits, any creature affected automatically succeeds on their save against the effect. Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you complete a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When a creature forces you or a friendly creature to make a saving throw, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Witcher 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"foil_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_17_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"f109fdf913a156a5ce2ab03a13a5ad4971e23761"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740321,"modifiedTime":1682004740321,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"LArSsYFhFrRgZaKR"}
{"name":"Evasion","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 15th level, you can nimbly dodge out of the way of certain area effects, such as a red dragon's fiery breath or a lightning bolt spell. When you are subjected to an effect that allows you to make a Dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, you instead take no damage if you succeed on the saving throw, and only half damage if you fail.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Witcher","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Witcher 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/light/beam-red-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"johnofbohemia:Witcher","hash":"evasion_witcher_johnofbohemia%3awitcher_15_johnofbohemia%3awitcher","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"2da06381b3fa302cf892e9c967fbe2309f9370db"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004740293,"modifiedTime":1682004740293,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"O9PwsG2LbUq7m9Uk"}
